Training Pipeline

# Run full training pipeline
python -m src.models.training_pipeline

# Or run individual steps:
python -m src.data.make_dataset           # Data preparation
python -m src.features.build_features     # Feature engineering
python -m src.models.train_model          # Model training
python -m src.models.evaluate_model       # Evaluation

Hyperparameter Optimization

# Run hyperparameter search with Optuna
python -m src.models.hyperparameter_tuning \
  --n_trials 100 \
  --study_name fraud_optimization

Monitoring & Observability
The system includes comprehensive monitoring:

Model Performance - Accuracy, precision, recall, AUC

Data Drift - Feature distribution changes

Prediction Drift - Score distribution monitoring

Service Metrics - Latency, throughput, error rates

Business Metrics - Fraud capture rate, false positives

Access dashboards at:

Grafana: http://localhost:3000

MLflow: http://localhost:5000

